	* ftpd.tcl: Imported changes made by "Gerald W. Lester"
	  <Gerald.Lester@ShowMaster.com>. Bugfixes, more callbacks (close,
	  transfer done), and implementation of passive mode data
	  connection. Version up to 1.2.

